node.text:
Who else love this moment? To celebrate @kamuikobayashi's birthday we thought this could be nice to watch again his amazing 3:14.791 Le Mans lap record done at the wheel of his @tgreurope LMP1 back in 2017. Oh and by the way, happy birthday to you Kamui.

#WEC #LeMans24 #Motorsport
